## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **MDMA-AT Lykos 2024 FDA reject** = first ever Phase 3 psychedelic-assisted therapy attempt FDA reject. data integrity (functional unblinding + therapist misconduct allegations) + trial design (concomitant therapy not separable from drug) issues. paradigm lessons for next-gen psychedelic-assisted therapy. quantum-VQE 의 5-HT2A + SERT next-gen scaffold fit.
2. **zuranolone Zurzuvae 2023** = first FDA oral neurosteroid (positive allosteric modulator GABA-A) PPD — 14-day course. brexanolone (Zulresso 2019) IV → zuranolone oral 진화. research GAD/MDD/PTSD adjunct. quantum-VQE 의 GABA-A allosteric pocket fit.
3. **esketamine Spravato 2019** = first FDA NMDA antagonist for TRD — intranasal. PTSD off-label + research. ketamine IV 의 isomer-selective 진화. quantum-VQE 의 NMDA glycine site / channel block dual fit.
4. **sertraline 1999 + paroxetine 2001** = only 2 FDA-approved drugs for PTSD. 25년 동안 추가 FDA PTSD approval 없음 (Lykos 2024 reject). drug development gap 심각.
5. **prazosin α1-AR PTSD nightmare** = decades off-label use → PACT 2018 large VA RCT null primary endpoint → 2018+ guideline downgrade. evidence-based + clinical practice 차이 paradigm.
6. **GABA-A BZD dependence + tolerance** = alprazolam/lorazepam/clonazepam/diazepam — FDA black-box 2020 dependence warning. PTSD VA/DoD guideline = avoid BZD. clinical practice 와 guideline 사이 큰 차이.
7. **SGA augmentation (risperidone/quetiapine/olanzapine/aripiprazole)** = PTSD adjunct off-label widely used but VA RCT 2011 risperidone primary negative. evidence-based downgrade.
8. **non-pharm 1L (PE + CPT + EMDR)** = VA/DoD + APA 1L PTSD = trauma-focused psychotherapy, NOT pharmacotherapy. drug-only treatment evidence-based 한계.
9. **K-PTSD 식약처 framework** = 한국 PTSD 임상 + 산정특례 + 한국 PTSD 등록 + 군인/소방관/경찰관 직업적 PTSD framework. 국내 sertraline + paroxetine 주력 + zuranolone 미진입.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, PTSD + anxiety specific 임상 의미 한정.

